spells.description: Equip: Your attacks have a chance to stir the larynx, allowing its dark whispers to influence you. Each whisper flows through your mind for 30 sec, granting 844 Strength.

Use: Wave the larynx in the air to release a tormenting chorus, inflicting 826,435 Shadow damage over 3 sec split between nearby enemies. Your whispers leave to join the chorus, increasing its damage before falling silent. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Your damaging spells and abilities have a chance to place a Spelunker's Candle on your head, granting 2,485 Critical Strike for 15 sec.

Moving within 3 yards of an ally places the Spelunker's Candle on both heads, sharing the effect for the remaining duration.
